{"tid":416057,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"汽水當水飲六年 浙江男幾盲","createTime":"2017-09-27T13:03:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T17:35:48.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"76c616b6fd682e6e20cf04667372cf26ae7b73ca","tid":416057,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T13:03:29.000Z","msg":"【本報綜合報道】浙江寧波廿五歲男子小凱，六年來將汽水當水喝，平時飲食亦不規律。他近日覺得視力變差遂到醫院檢查，未料竟發現患上糖尿病視網膜病變末期，右眼視力只有0.05，左眼甚至幾乎全盲。醫生指出，雖然可進行手術治療，但無法完全恢復視力。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，小凱求診時血糖已超標。他指自己因經常加班，所以平日飲食並不規律，而且都只喝飲料；最初發現視力開始模糊，還以為是加班疲勞所致，沒想到竟如此嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n手術只能挽回部分視力<br />\n醫生指出，小凱雙眼的玻璃體出血，且眼底新生血管大量增生，整個視網膜發生牽拉性脫離，引發白內障。小凱需要立即控制血糖，隨後再進行手術治療，但由於糖尿病視網膜病變造成的損害屬永久性，故只能挽回部分視力<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170923/00178_024.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170923%2F00178_024.html&d=WsmKV74dZ2wOEB46lhTzW4S5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=b857dc3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170923/00178_024.html</a>"},{"pid":"84f68129f6c6ce3ed9b3daea694eb42368c57b45","tid":416057,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T13:05:33.000Z","msg":"六年先出事已經超出正常人數值"},{"pid":"a604680ea85a23a9ed92731aaeb1b8df9dcccff5","tid":416057,"uid":146924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T13:30:34.000Z","msg":"每日隊2-3包紙包飲品會唔會有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7244f8b4eb74d70cae1a21c171765f0f27e2d8da","tid":416057,"uid":72173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T13:37:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每日隊2-3包紙包飲品會唔會有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇糖份啦，或者睇番運動量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}